      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/35428890/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_8477632232918351020.png",
                "id": "talent83493",
                "key": "Cicin Icicle",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cicin Icicle"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span>, summons <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Cryo Cicins</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/35428890/1a979041a9881649ba69332b20dd5820_4769566871087296685.png",
                "id": "talent88436",
                "key": "Misty Summons",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Misty Summons"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 5 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>, grants this character <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo Application</span>, creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Flowing Cicin Shield</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Flowing Cicin Shield</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Combat Status</span></p><p>Provides <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">1 Shield point</span> for your active character.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">When created</span>: If you have <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Cryo Cicins</span> on the field, additionally increase <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Shield </span>by the amount of Usage(s) it has. (Adds a maximum of 3 additional <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Shield</span>)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/35428890/8d60085e1f79ee9a2bb87006d7f2d32c_1908652300750240211.png",
                "id": "talent65236",
                "key": "Blizzard, Branch, Blossom",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Blizzard, Branch, Blossom"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase</span>: Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 2</span> (Can stack, max 3 stacks)</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After Fatui Cryo Cicin Mage performs a Normal Attack</span>: This card gains 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After Fatui Cryo Cicin Mage takes Elemental Reaction DMG</span>:This card loses 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_771206739104048301.png",
                "id": "talent27591",
                "key": "Cryo Cicins",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/35428890/1467dd7dd3fec80047e77cc996621508_8658085116606653871.png",
                "title": "Cryo Cicins"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Cryo and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG+1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives Physical or Pyro DMG, in which case they will take +2 DMG)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/35428890/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_437254943583064410.png",
                "id": "talent17886",
                "key": "Cryo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cryo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Shield</span></strong></p><p>This Shield will be consumed to protect the character who equips it from DMG.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo Application</span></strong></p><p>When Cryo is applied without dealing any DMG, the Elemental Reaction triggered will ignore DMG-dealing effects:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: No effect</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: No effect</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: The target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives Physical or Pyro DMG, in which case they will take +2 DMG)</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_5400960070547252978.png",
